This paper discusses the practical implementation of GraphQL in web-based APIs, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) category. It also involves database (cs.DB) and web (cs.WEB) technologies. Additionally, it may be relevant to programming languages (cs.PL) and information retrieval (cs.IR) as GraphQL is a query language and involves data retrieval.
